OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FA teacher at a #36,000 a year boarding
OL,7,Fschool has been struck off after
OL,8,Frepeatedly declaring his love to a
OL,9,Fpupil.
OL,11,FBenjamin Phelps, 31, was banned from
OL,12,Fteaching indefinitely after a
OL,13,Fdisciplinary panel found he committed
OL,14,Fserious misconduct by his relationship
OL,15,Fwith a student at St Bede's School,
OL,16,Fnear Hailsham in East Sussex.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
