CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FAt the time he worked as a deputy
OL,7,Fboarding housemaster, tutor and
OL,8,Fperforming arts technician at its
OL,9,Fsenior school for students aged 13 to
OL,10,F18.
OL,12,FDuring their relationship, Mr Phelps
OL,13,Ftexted the pupil inappropriately, they
OL,14,Fmet up outside lessons, hugged and
OL,15,Fkissed on the cheek, and he requested
OL,16,Fthey skip school to "eat in the car"
OL,17,Ftogether.
OL,26,@xD@UOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
