PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FHe was fired in April 2024 following
OL,7,Fan investigation and the Teaching
OL,8,FRegulation Agency's professional
OL,9,Fconduct panel struck him off on
OL,10,FJanuary 16 this year.
OL,12,FOne WhatsApp message he sent said: "I
OL,13,Fhope you've had a good night, I'm
OL,14,Ffalling asleep with my phone in my
OL,15,Fhand. I love you and wish you sweet
OL,16,Fdream!! Contact me about anything
OL,17,Fxxxxxx".
OL,26,@tD@dOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
