CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FAnother said: "A hot feeling went
OL,7,Fthrough me, from front to back, I
OL,8,Fshook slightly (bit weird but true),
OL,9,Fthen I had this warm glow and I can't
OL,10,Fstop staring at it.
OL,12,F"I feel love, like pure love at a
OL,13,Flevel I'm not sure I've felt before.
OL,14,FThis one feels special. (I'm so sorry
OL,15,Ffor this but you want the truth) it
OL,16,Fproperly turned me on.
OL,26,@nD@OOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
