PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,F"I just want to grab you and pick you
OL,7,Fup and have you wrapped around me.
OL,8,FAlso (less crass now!) I feel like
OL,9,Fthere is not a single other thought in
OL,10,Fmy brain, not one other than you."
OL,12,FHe also told the student: "Love you
OL,13,Fmore every day. My heart fluttered
OL,14,Fevery time you caught my eye x also, I
OL,15,Flove the hearts! Just ready them
OL,16,Fthey'll stay close to me xx".
OL,18,FOn one occasion he wrote on a napkin:
OL,19,F"Just to say.. I (heart symbol) with
OL,20,Fall my (heart symbol), xxxx, missed
OL,21,Fyou today".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]tD@[OUxD@\O]{D@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
