PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FMr Phelps received a call from the
OL,7,Fpupil in October 2023 and their
OL,8,Frelationship became increasingly
OL,9,Fpersonal between November and January
OL,10,F2024, shown in messages sent on the
OL,11,Fschool's main system for digital
OL,12,Fcommunication.
OL,14,FThese Google chat messages, scattered
OL,15,Fwith kisses and emojis, included "you
OL,16,Fhave such a beautiful mind though,
OL,17,Fit's so pure and genuine, I've always
OL,18,Fsaid that", "massive hugs on the
OL,19,Fpillow" and "maybe delete this chat
OL,20,Ftoo in case they look through your
OL,21,Fphone".
OL,26,@wD@bOUzD@JO]zD@MOU{D@GO]{D@MOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
