PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FThe student disclosed a matter to him
OL,7,Fin November 2023 that should have
OL,8,Fprompted him to follow safeguarding
OL,9,Fprocedures but he did not, the panel
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FHe moved their correspondence to
OL,13,FWhatsApp in January 2024, which was
OL,14,Fnot a school-approved form of
OL,15,Fcommunication, and they spent more
OL,16,Ftime together outside of lessons and
OL,17,Fexchanged photographs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
