OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FTheir relationship "came to a head"
OL,7,Fwhen the student attempted to kiss Mr
OL,8,FPhelps in February 2024, the panel
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FIt was indicated that the teacher did
OL,12,Fnot reciprocate the kiss and he then
OL,13,Fattempted to return their relationship
OL,14,Fto "a more professional footing", it
OL,15,Ffound.
OL,17,FHowever he did not report the kiss and
OL,18,Faccepted to the tribunal that there
OL,19,Fhad on occasion been kisses on the
OL,20,Fcheek.
OL,26,@nD@TOUnD@cO]vD@DOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
