PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FReferences to hugs in their messages
OL,7,Fmade it clear that "hugs had occurred
OL,8,Fbetween them", the panel said.
OL,10,FDuring the hearing, Mr Phelps
OL,11,F"conceded that with hindsight he had
OL,12,Fprobably been flattered to receive the
OL,13,Fattention" and that some messages he
OL,14,Fsent "indicated that he had developed
OL,15,Fromantic feelings".
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@MO]sD@AOUuD@JO]vD@FOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
