OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FThe panel found "both individually and
OL,7,Fcumulatively the activities" amounted
OL,8,Fto "significant breaches of
OL,9,Fprofessional boundaries and
OL,10,Fdemonstrated that by February 2024 the
OL,11,Frelationship between Mr Phelps and
OL,12,FPupil A had become personal and
OL,13,Fromanticised".
OL,15,FAn allegation that he pursued a
OL,16,F"course of conduct akin to grooming"
OL,17,Fwas not proved.
OL,26,@nD@QOUoD@\O]pD@DOUuD@MO]xD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
