PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774264485
OL,3,CMarried teacher struck off after
OL,4,Crepeatedly telling pupil "I love you"
OL,6,FMr Phelps can apply for the
OL,7,Fprohibition order to be set aside but
OL,8,Fnot until January 2030, and he has a
OL,9,Fright of appeal at the High Court.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
